message:
We've added a mentorship program to Spinal Implants Identification Group so you can build skills and share knowledge with another member of our community. I am excited to see all of us build stronger relationships with each other and hope you'll join.

Here's how the program works:

You sign up, match yourself with a partner, and get helpful conversation starters each week so you get to know each other better. It's up to you how much time you want to spend together and what goals you want to work towards.

https://www.facebook.com/fbmentorship/signup/?application_id=1366267283538739
